Package: artoo
Title: Versatile Lossless Port for Clinical Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Vignesh", "Thanikachalam", , "about.vignesh@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Reads and writes clinical-trial datasets losslessly across
    SAS XPORT (XPT), CDISC Dataset-JSON, and Apache Parquet, applying a
    specification to produce submission-ready SDTM and ADaM datasets. A
    single canonical metadata model carries labels, CDISC data types,
    lengths, SAS display formats, controlled-terminology references, and
    sort keys identically across every format, so conversion between any
    two formats is lossless by construction. Pure R and lightweight, with
    no external 'SAS' or 'Java' runtime.
